{id:"animal-handling",name:"Animal Handling",content:[{id:"Title",content:"Animal Handling"},{id:"StatGrid",content:[{title:"Ability",content:"@wis"}]},{id:"MultiText",content:["When there is any question whether you can calm down a domesticated animal, keep a mount from getting spooked, or intuit an animal's intentions, the GM might call for a Wisdom (Animal Handling) check. You also make a Wisdom (Animal Handling) check to control your mount when you attempt a risky maneuver."]}]}